The sets here are wonderful and the mood is engaging.  The dancing, however, didn't work for me.  Let me emphasize that I'm not an expert so this is purely an idiosyncratic, lay person review.  But I found that the dancing was too repetitive and predominately arm-movement oriented.  It just failed to hold my attention the way my other dance videos do.  A friend who popped by and watched a bit of it, commented spontaneously about the same thing.  Not bad, just not to my liking.

Out of the dozens of "hentai" titles I've watched over the last few months, this one was probably the worst. In fact, it annoyed me so much that I'm actually taking the time to write a review so that others don't make the same mistake I did by buying it.

I never really cared much for detailed storylines in a porno, and this is pretty much why. It's a porno, not Forrest Gump. I just want what I came here for, and this title could barely even deliver that. The sex scenes were scarce, and what little there was, was mediocre. This was one of those very annoying pornos where the sex scenes show almost exclusively the guy the whole time, and all of the stupid faces he is making. Want to see naked women? You won't find it in this title. If you came here looking for close-up shots of guys' private parts and them making stupid faces, then this title might be for you. The "storyline" was nothing to behold, and it shouldn't be anyway. They were trying too hard, and failed.

This was quite possibly the worst hentai I've ever seen. I would not recommend this title to anyone.
